[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說希有挍量功德經",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隋天竺三藏闍那崛多譯",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，長老阿難比丘在蘭若處獨坐思惟，作如是念：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸善男子及善女人，若能受持三歸依處，作如是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』得幾所功德？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」生是念已，長老阿難日初出時於其住處，即從坐起齊整衣裳，安詳而出，往詣佛所。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "到佛所已，頂禮佛足，偏袒右肩，右膝著地，合掌向佛，而作是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c13_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我於向者在空閑處，如是思惟：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『若善男子及善女人，能如是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」得幾所功德？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』我實未解，惟願如來分別演說，令諸眾生得正知見。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊告阿難言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝善男子真實智慧微妙能善思量，能問如來如斯之義。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝思量，彼善男子及善女人若能清淨發如是心：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』得幾所功德者，諦聽，諦聽！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善思念之！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾當為汝分別解說。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯然。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願樂欲聞。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c23_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊告阿難言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此閻浮提地縱廣七千由旬，形如車葙南狹北廣，假使滿中須陀洹人，譬如竹葦、甘蔗、稻麻。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0783c26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一切須陀洹人，其有善男子、善女人，滿一百年，持於世間一切所有娛樂之具，盡給施與，復以四事具足供養恭敬禮拜，乃至滅度之後，收其舍利起七寶塔，一一塔廟皆以香華、蘇油、燈燭，作倡伎樂，繒綵、幡蓋種種供養。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼善男子、善女人得福多不？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚多。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a03_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如是善男子、善女人，以淳淨心，作如是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』所得功德，於彼福德百分不及一，千分不及一，百千萬分不及一，乃至算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復告阿難：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且置閻浮提。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使西瞿陀尼縱廣八千由旬，其地形狀猶如半月，皆悉滿中斯陀含人，譬如竹葦、甘蔗、稻麻。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人滿二百年，復以世間種種四事，供養如前，乃至滅度之後，收其舍利起七寶塔，一一寶塔，亦以華香、燈燭、伎樂、繒蓋、幢幡種種供養。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼善男子、善女人得福多不？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚多。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a16_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如是善男子、善女人以淳淨心，作如是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』所得功德，於彼福德百分不及一，千分不及一，億分不及一，百千億分不及一，乃至算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復告阿難：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且置一閻浮提、一瞿陀尼。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使東弗婆提縱廣九千由旬，其地形狀猶如滿月，皆悉滿中阿那含人，譬如竹葦、甘蔗、稻麻。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人滿三百年，復以四事一切樂具，供養如前，乃至滅度之後，收其舍利起七寶塔，一一寶塔，皆以華香、伎樂、幡蓋，種種供養。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼善男子、善女人得福多不？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚多。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784a29_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如是善男子善女人，以淳淨心作如是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』所得功德，於彼福德百分不及一，千分不及一，百千分不及一，億分不及一，百億分不及一，百千億分不及一，乃至算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復告阿難：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且置一閻浮提、一瞿陀尼、一弗婆提。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使北方欝單羅越，縱廣十千由旬，其地形狀四方端直，周匝齊整，滿中阿羅漢，諸漏已盡，無復煩惱，心得自在，具正解脫，正智得解脫，其心調伏，人中大龍，所作已辦，捨棄重擔，逮得自利，不受後有，梵行已立，身心無礙，達眾生意，得六神通、具八解脫，譬如竹葦、甘蔗、稻麻。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人滿四百年，復以四事供養恭敬，一切樂具給足如前，乃至滅度之後起七寶塔，一一寶塔，皆以華香、伎樂、燈燭、繒蓋、幢幡，種種供養。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b16_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼善男子、善女人得福多不？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚多。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b18_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如是善男子、善女人以淳淨心，作如是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』所得功德，於前福德百分不及一，千分不及一，百千分不及一，百千億分不及一，乃至算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復告阿難：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且置閻浮提、瞿陀尼、弗婆提、欝單羅越。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使遍四天下，滿中辟支佛獨覺，譬如竹葦、甘蔗、稻麻。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人滿十千年，復以四事供養恭敬，一切樂具給足如前，乃至滅度之後，收其舍利起七寶塔，一一寶塔，皆以華香、伎樂、燈燭、繒蓋、幢幡，種種供養。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784b29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼善男子、善女人得福多不？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚多。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c01_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如是善男子、善女人以淳淨心，作如是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』所得功德，於前福德百分不及一，千分不及一，百千分不及一，百千億分不及一，乃至算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復告阿難：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且置一四天下，一日月光所照之處。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設復一千世界，所謂一千日月、一千四大海水、一千須彌山王、一千閻浮提、一千瞿陀尼、一千弗婆提、一千欝單羅越、一千四天王天、一千三十三天、一千夜摩天、一千珊兜率陀天、一千化自樂天、一千他化自在天、一千梵天，不相繫屬，各於千世界中得大自在。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名一小千世界。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從一小千世界，一一數之滿一千已，是名中千世界。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從中千世界，復一一數還滿一千，是名大千世界。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是合數總名三千大千世界。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c18_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使滿三千大千世界中諸佛如來，譬如竹葦、甘蔗、稻麻，彼等諸佛、世尊、至真、等正覺。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人二萬歲中，常以一切娛樂之具，衣服、飲食、床臥、湯藥，種種奉施，乃至滅度之後，收其舍利起七寶塔，一一寶塔，皆以華香、伎樂、繒蓋、幢幡、香燭、油燈，如是供養。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼善男子及善女人得福多不？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚多。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告阿難：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0784c25_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若復有人直能供養一佛世尊，滿二萬歲，四事具足供養恭敬，乃至滅度收其舍利，起七寶塔，一一寶塔，皆以華香、伎樂、幡蓋、香油、燈燭，一切奉施其福尚多，無量無邊不可稱數，何況滿三千大千世界諸佛如來！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二萬歲中常以四事供養供給，乃至滅度，收其舍利，起七寶塔，一一寶塔，各以華香、伎樂、幡蓋及香油燈，種種所須悉皆供養，實得無量無邊、不可算、不可數福德之聚。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶不如是善男子、善女人以淳淨心，作如是言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今歸依佛、歸依法、歸依僧。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』所得功德勝前福德，百倍、千倍、萬倍，不可算數、言辭譬類所能知及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復告阿難：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若有人能歸依佛竟、歸依法竟、歸依僧竟，乃至一彈指頃能受十善，受已修行，以是因緣得無量無邊功德。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a12_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有人能一日一夜，受八戒齋已，如說修行，所得功德勝前福德，千倍、萬倍、百千萬倍，乃至算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能受持五戒盡其形壽，如說修行，所得功德勝前福德，百倍、千倍、萬倍、千億萬倍，非算數、譬喻所能知及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有人受沙彌戒、沙彌尼戒，復勝於前百倍、千倍、萬倍、千億萬倍，非算數、譬喻所能知及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「阿難！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有人能受持式叉摩那戒，又復所得功德，勝前福德百倍、千倍、百千萬倍，乃至算數、譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何況受持比丘尼戒，依波羅提木叉如說修行！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "況復有人盡形受持大比丘戒，依波羅提木叉戒如說修行，不缺不犯無有穢濁，清淨梵行，得無量無邊功德，勝前百倍、千倍、萬倍、百千萬倍，乃至算數、譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785a27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，長老阿難聞佛說此三歸依處，乃至盡壽護大比丘波羅提木叉，功德無量，歎未曾有，白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚奇！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是經微妙不可思議，明甚深義，功德廣大難可校量。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當何名此經？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等云何奉持？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告阿難：",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此經名為『希有希有經』，汝當奉持。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是經中說希有之法，所演勝法一切世間難聞，故名希有。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說是經已，長老阿難，聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說希有挍量功德經",
        "from": "T16n0690_001:0785b08_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]